  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><span>Each morning there's a buffet breakfast with eggs, pastries, cereals, fresh fruit, toast with honey or jam, juices and coffee. </span></p>
<p><span>You can upgrade to half board and eat at the hotel each evening. </span>The view from the restaurant is amazing! During the day you can see right across the bay and in the evening the twinkling Positano lights.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
