  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel L'Ancora has some of the best views in Positano. The panoramic terrace looks out across the colourful town and the bay. It's just a short walk to town and the beach and a great base for exploring the sights of the Amalfi Coast.</p>]]></listingDescription>
